" Normal mode mappings

" Disable arrow keys to help learn to rely on home row
nnoremap <left> <nop>
nnoremap <right> <nop>
nnoremap <up> <nop>
nnoremap <down> <nop>

" Split navigation
" nnoremap <C-h> <C-w>h
" nnoremap <C-j> <C-w>j
" nnoremap <C-k> <C-w>k
" nnoremap <C-l> <C-w>l

" Prefer to yank from cursor to end of line rather than entire line
noremap Y y$
